{"tid":508056,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人到三十，沒有朋友","createTime":"2017-12-24T00:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T08:20:56.000Z","uid":6866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef2af8e0a616d5054fb2c9eaa8ab2da2ee5fb6b","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"人到三十，一個真心朋友都冇<br />\n是否好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學果時都好精靈，活躍<br />\n身邊都叫有十個八個朋友仔<br />\n放假會一齊落公園蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n諗起都好撚過癮"},{"pid":"5273f3874e3bd94e6f327a168700264c5cec5177","tid":508056,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"我看到我的影子"},{"pid":"22bdbc0eacbec22aa7047b4ee340f6f229c95d85","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:49:32.000Z","msg":"到中學，我覺得呢段期間係影響得最最最大<br />\n因為跟阿哥入左間brand 1（全港最top堆）<br />\n去到一個完全陌生既環境，好唔習慣<br />\n而且果到d人真係好勁，無論個人能力，屋企背景<br />\n所以一開始，我都唔太出聲，默默地認真讀左一個學期書。<br />\n結果，我呢個靠&rdquo;哥陰&rdquo;既毒撚，成績係最尾果20%<br />\n我開始明白到，讀書都係講天份。"},{"pid":"ee36aff9a531e125b377b3e680d7ab7ba67a5fe5","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5273f3874e3bd94e6f327a168700264c5cec5177","tid":508056,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"我看到我的影子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"你～最近還好嗎"},{"pid":"b5cb51845bff649391c1859e4bb50957a7b2ffaa","tid":508056,"uid":163656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ef2af8e0a616d5054fb2c9eaa8ab2da2ee5fb6b","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"人到三十，一個真心朋友都冇<br />\n是否好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學果時都好精靈，活躍<br />\n身邊都叫有十個八個朋友仔<br />\n放假會一齊落公園蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n諗起都好撚過癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"人唔需要有朋友<br />\n搵狗做朋友"},{"pid":"a3fb8554adb1a01b58d59a9306703ef8693abadc","tid":508056,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a484e26b24303a94dce2f9a2b2b3a671b0aec6","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:58:57.000Z","msg":"所以我決定做番小學既我<br />\n上堂搞下笑，駁下老師嘴<br />\n慢慢地，開始同幾個成績較差既friend左<br />\n<br />\n另一方面都有搵番班小學同學<br />\n佢地大部分都入左同一間中學<br />\n見到佢地依然咁精靈，我都高興既<br />\n但又有種遠離感<br />\n原來我開始埋唔到堆"},{"pid":"2b816d4a7b37ca2509cd4b13332c30237d6c5328","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T01:08:12.000Z","msg":"班小同亦都開始少左約我<br />\n可能佢地覺得我入左間好中學，唔識人<br />\n但其實我係好唔開心，收埋緊自己<br />\n如果可以，我想跟埋佢地同一間中學<br />\n至少可以減少煩惱先"},{"pid":"61d649edbf614db93cc65bc74465dec4eadbb099","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"每日過住小丑既生活<br />\n上堂就嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n落堂就去網吧<br />\n同學關係都改善左好多<br />\n<br />\n漸漸開始有學校團體活動<br />\n期間同個女仔互相產生左好感<br />\n好快再小圈子約出來玩"},{"pid":"bae86081430897d60f606071e387e9cdab227d62","tid":508056,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f8e0e1f2b24ac184218a9b5eec5bc0c00cea999","tid":508056,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"然後呢？"},{"pid":"28f7a3ecbdaf7a89fc9a9ceb4410687d8dc1f5e5","tid":508056,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f8e0e1f2b24ac184218a9b5eec5bc0c00cea999","tid":508056,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"然後呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"然後呢？"},{"pid":"dcf40e8b820dae18e691639837dd88573da24061","tid":508056,"uid":21355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/1c/Xmas_ani.gif/revision/latest?cb=20101222080729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F1c%2FXmas_ani.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101222080729&h=93e2378b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222d6890822a18fe47ac2c4086c48679061a372c","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"一班人有男有女既活動，先係惡夢既開始<br />\n因為第一次私約，大家都好注重自己既打扮<br />\n我都知道呢一點，但無奈毒撚唔識襯衫，亦無錢買衫<br />\n所以著套運動裝出去，心諗我行黃祖藍路線架麻<br />\n但出到來，個個都潮童咁款<br />\n大家互相欣賞，呢件買左幾錢，果件係邊個國家買<br />\n我就成為左謝師宴毒男<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/143742_56ed6385952b27528a64c14c6e3a326e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F143742_56ed6385952b27528a64c14c6e3a326e.jpeg&h=7a9c37f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"849e3e4259295222c4f241da271ee8518d8e345b","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"而之前有好感既女同學，亦都開始疏遠我<br />\n我終於明白到咩是贏在起跑線<br />\n回望番自己屋企，父母係採用放牧政策<br />\n對我地兩兄弟係天生天養咁<br />\n每星期比抵$150 食飯+搭車<br />\n<br />\n換季要買新衫<br />\n你識咩擇丫！<br />\n冇穿冇爛，仲著得！<br />\n之後去街市買d毒撚衫<br />\n<br />\n想學抬拳、想要玩具、想要ps，<br />\n你成績好好咩？讀好d書先啦<br />\n<br />\n每日番到屋企都係得種冷冰冰的感覺"},{"pid":"9b87167180589570699bbbf549c829f40177e53a","tid":508056,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"至此之後，我變得好毒好毒好毒<br />\n每日上堂都係訓覺<br />\n我唔係因為累先訓覺<br />\n我係想逃避<br />\n我開始唔識點同人相處<br />\n我覺得成班同學都恥笑緊我<br />\n<br />\n老師見我冇搞搞震，亦都冇再理我<br />\n慢慢我被編到單行位<br />\n我試過大病一場，休息左成個月<br />\n番到班房，係冇人理我<br />\n我已經不屬於任何一個地方"},{"pid":"5c636132f205d704ecb57eca52027ea4da314fd4","tid":508056,"uid":4425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"a030a1ddf5a7420bb1935e77bb0deb562605f9f4","tid":508056,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"真心定假膠<br />\n有冇咁灰丫"}]}